# Valacme

A modern implementation of the Plan 9 Acme editor using Vala and GTK4.

## Overview

Valacme tries to be a faithful port of the Acme editor from the Plan 9 operating system to modern Linux desktop environments.

## Requirements

- Vala compiler
- GTK4
- Meson
- Ninja

## Building

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/lainsce/valacme.git
cd valacme

# Build with Meson
meson setup builddir
cd builddir
ninja

# Run the application
./valacme
```